---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="Backend engineering, database support, and AI/RAG backend practice.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>Backend and database engineering experience with ongoing AI/RAG backend practice, focusing on the full path from data and APIs to deployment, logs, monitoring, and operations.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="two-column">
    <div>
      <h2>Direction</h2>
      <p>This site is my personal project lab and technical review archive. It records backend engineering, database practice, AI/RAG experiments, deployment, observability, and tooling notes.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <p>Nearly 3 years of database support and backend-related work, with practical experience in deployment, monitoring, logs, load testing, database inspection, and operations support.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Stack</p>
        <h2>Technical Stack</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Backend, databases, and AI/RAG engineering.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="skill-grid">
      <div class="skill-card">
        <span>Languages</span>
        <strong>Python / SQL</strong>
        <p>Python for backend services, data workflows, scripts, and AI/RAG project practice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <span>Backend</span>
        <strong>FastAPI / SQLAlchemy / Pydantic</strong>
        <p>API design, data models, validation, async tasks, and maintainable service structure.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <span>Data</span>
        <strong>PostgreSQL / MySQL / Redis</strong>
        <p>Database inspection, DDL maintenance, stored procedures, cache usage, and data issue diagnosis.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <span>AI Backend</span>
        <strong>pgvector / TaskIQ / PydanticAI / Langfuse</strong>
        <p>RAG, vector search, task orchestration, evaluation, tracing, and AI backend implementation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <span>Ops</span>
        <strong>Linux / Docker / GitHub Actions / GCP / AWS</strong>
        <p>Deployment, environment configuration, CI/CD, log troubleshooting, and basic cloud resources.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <span>Observability</span>
        <strong>Prometheus / Grafana / Loki</strong>
        <p>Metrics, logs, dashboards, and runtime visibility after deployment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
